OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1774973461
OL,3,CStarmer gives resident doctors 48-hour
OL,4,Cdeadline to call off 'reckless' strikes
OL,6,FSir Keir Starmer has issued resident
OL,7,Fdoctors an ultimatum to call off their
OL,8,Fstrikes, or face losing the deal
OL,9,Falready on the table.
OL,11,FThe prime minister gave the British
OL,12,FMedical Association (BMA) 48 hours to
OL,13,Fwithdraw its threat of strikes, or
OL,14,Felse threatened to withdraw an offer
OL,15,Fof thousands of extra specialty NHS
OL,16,Ftraining posts.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
